**Story:**

There was once a wood nymph called Echo. She alway liked to gossip to the other wood nymphs. eventually, the goddess Hera got tired of her gossip, and punished her to only be able to repeat the last thing another person said. Eventually, after a long while of wandering, Echo came upon a man named Narcissus. She fell in love, and they had an awkward converstation with each other. 
